# Token used by the /api/bugs route (server-side only) to create GitHub issues.
# It is NEVER sent to the browser — do not prefix it with VITE_.
#
# Use ONE of:
#   - a classic Personal Access Token with the "repo" scope, or
#   - a fine-grained token with "Issues: Read and write" on each target repo:
#       FoodimeRepo/foodime, soundmade-com/soundmade-old, wewaive/wewaive, kiibee-app/kiibee
#
# After setting this, restart the dev server.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
